Package api.equinix.javasdk.core.client

package api.equinix.javasdk.core.client
Core client infrastructure for the Equinix Java SDK. Contains the Config interface that defines the contract for domain-specific configuration classes, and the EquinixClient base class that manages HTTP communication, OAuth token lifecycle, and API parameter loading. The ClientBase provides request-building utilities, while PageableBase adds pagination support for internal client implementations.
